s/1735691254464135580">有传言</a>称欧洲价格约为 400 欧元（430 美元），部分原因是更便宜的 MediaTek Dimensity 7200 处理器。</p><p>同样的传言表明，它将有一个简化的界面，更少的 LED 灯条，再加上顶部居中的双摄像头，就像头上的眼睛一样（正如<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/13/24070423/nothing-phone-2a-launch-event-march-5th-us-release-developer-program"><em>The Verge</em></a>指出的那样，Nothing 的“通过新的眼睛看世界”在某种程度上支持了这一点）。 Nothing 的发布视频中显示的草图似乎支持了这一说法。我们可能很快就会了解到更多信息，因为Nothing 将于 2 月 27 日在巴塞罗那举行世界移动大会 (MWC) 新闻发布会。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nothings-phone-2a-will-debut-on-march-5-123559888.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nothings-phone-2a-will-debut-on-march-5-123559888.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cb9ddfcf-2cce-4f4a-9a82-e9c00176fc70 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Steve Dent]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:35:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707825968</ingested><modified> 2024-02-13T12:06:13+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F2ff21e70-ca5d-11ee-83ff-834540de7687&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=c126586588ac70be59319ba86b99edd67ea413d9" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media: